    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s41562-024-02077-2",
    "On each trial, an array of 12 emotional faces, ranging from sad to happy, was presented for 500 ms (Fig. 1a).",
    "The participants indicated whether, on average, the faces were more happy or more sad.",
